      <lg xml:id="ATA39">
<l>kompiṉaiyōr pākattuk koṇṭa kuḻakaṉta</l>
<l>ṉampavaḷa mēṉi yatumuṉṉañ - cempoṉ</l>
<l>ṉaṇivaraiyē pōlum poṭiyaṇintāl veḷḷi</l>
<l>maṇivaraiyē pōlu maṟittu</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The front of the pretty coral body of the young one who takes a twig</l>
<l>as one part, resembles a mountain adorned with red gold.</l>
<l>When it is adorned with ashes, it changes [and] resembles</l>
<l>a silver [and] pearl mountain.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
